Discworld player help
meditate

.SH Name
.SI 5
meditate - Change your position to meditating.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
meditate
meditate on [the] floor
meditate [on|at|beside] <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to change your position.  To meditate on the floor, or to
meditate on, at or beside something.  However, meditating at certain 
holy places could cause some unexpected effects.
.EP


.SH Examples
.SI 5
> meditate
You meditate.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
kneel, stand, lie, sit, crouch
.EP
